author: wn.com
title: Mergers: Commission signs best practices cooperation framework with China (European Commission)
text: ( Source : European Commission ) The European Commission 's competition department and the Ministry of Commerce (Mofcom) of the People's Republic of China have signed today in Beijing best practices for cooperation on reviewing mergers.
